		"name": "Orders",
		"description": "### **Orders API - Description**\n\nThe **Orders API** processes customer orders including **placing, retrieving, and deleting orders**.\n\n### **Available Endpoints:**\n\n✔️ `GET /orders` → Fetch all orders\n\n✔️ `GET /orders/:id` → Get order details\n\n✔️ `POST /orders` → Place a new order\n\n✔️ `DELETE /orders/:id` → Cancel an order\n\n**Validation Rules:**  \n✅ **User ID:** Must exist in the system  \n✅ **Product ID:** Must exist in the system  \n✅ **Quantity:** Integer between 1 - 10\n\n**Common Errors & Status Codes:**\n\n- `400 Bad Request` → Invalid input or quantity\n    \n- `404 Not Found` → Order/User/Product not found",
